name: Go Cube Go
description:
A casual game where you have to prove your reflects. Dodge obstacles, select the correct color and pick up Power Ups to help you in this infinity journey.

Power Ups:

* Immunity - Nothing can hurt you! (at least for seconds).
* Change colors constantly and pass for any ligth without import the color.

Obstacles:
* The light where you go through must be the same as the current color of the cube.
* The green walls dont be touched.
* There is a gigant cube that move. Be careful.
* Cylindrs scattered on the path. you musnt touch them too.

Do not forget log in on Google Play Games for compete on the Ranking and gets achievements! If you could ...

Have Fun !
